headline: Dow Jones Tops 50,000 With Apple, Boeing, These AI Stocks New Buys, But Market Still Divided
summary: The Dow Jones topped 50,000 for the first time, with JPMorgan, Apple and Boeing in buy areas. The Nasdaq is ailing, but these AI stocks are reviving.

headline: Boeing Faces New Jet Issues While International Orders Test Recovery Story
summary: New technical issues have emerged on Boeing's (NYSE:BA) widebody jets, including GE9X engine problems on the 777X and a fuel control switch defect on the 787 Dreamliner, leading to groundings and additional regulatory attention. Boeing has halted F-15 fighter jet production for Indonesia after a proposed deal did not move forward.
